  <summary date="2021-07-21T14:30:08Z" status="Introduced in House">Taxpayers and Savers Protection Act or the TSP Act

This bill prohibits any sums in the Thrift Savings Fund from being invested in a security that is listed on an exchange in a jurisdiction in which the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board is prevented from conducting the mandatory inspection or investigation of a registered public accounting firm because of a position taken by an authority in that jurisdiction.</summary>
